<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Inicio | Yato</title>
    <%- include('components/head.ejs') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style/pages/index.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('components/header.ejs') %>

    <section class="hero flex">
      <div class="content container-lg m-auto">
        <h2 class="title-3 container-sm font-bold font-action">
          Cadastre-se para <br />saber sobre:
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-hero">
          <li class="list-hero-item">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined list-hero-icon title-1">
              help
            </span>
            <span class="list-hero-text font-lg font-action hover-underline">
              O Por Quê da Escolha
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-hero-item">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined list-hero-icon title-1">
              person_search
            </span>
            <span class="list-hero-text font-lg font-action hover-underline">
              Sobre o Personagem
            </span>
          </li>
          <li class="list-hero-item">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined list-hero-icon title-1">
              notes
            </span>
            <span class="list-hero-text font-lg font-action hover-underline">
              Detalhes e Clips
            </span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <button class="button font-xlg">cadastrar</button>
      </div>
      <div class="box-detail">
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
        <div class="point-detail"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <main>
      <section class="main-features container-lg m-auto mt-section">
        <h2 class="title-2 font-bold font-action point-detail-after mb">
          Principais funcionalidades
        </h2>

        <section class="cards mt flex align-center flex-between">
          <div class="card card-md shadow-blur-1">
            <h4 class="card-md-title title-1">Métricas</h4>
            <ul class="card-md-list font-md">
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Clips mais favoritados
              </li>
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Quantidade de usuários
              </li>
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Média de idade dos usuários
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-main">
            <h4 class="card-main-title title-2 font-bold">Clips</h4>
            <ul class="card-main-list font-lg">
              <li class="card-main-item point-detail-after">Criar Clip</li>
              <li class="card-main-item point-detail-after">Favoritar Clip</li>
              <li class="card-main-item point-detail-after">
                Ver Clips de outros
              </li>
              <li class="card-main-item point-detail-after">
                Fazer comentários
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card card-md">
            <h4 class="card-md-title title-1">Acesso</h4>
            <ul class="card-md-list font-md">
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Sobre o personagem
              </li>
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Biografia e detalhes
              </li>
              <li class="card-md-item point-detail-after">
                Por quê da escolha
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>

      <section class="comments mt-section">
        <div class="container-lg m-auto">
          <h2 class="title-2 font-bold font-action point-detail-after mb">
            Comentários
          </h2>
        </div>

        <section class="flex flex-around align-center">
          <div
            class="comment text-center flex-center flex align-center flex-column"
          >
            <h4 class="font-lg font-bold underline comment-title">
              Fernando Brandão
            </h4>
            <div class="comment-body font-xsm">
              “O conteudo do site está completo e as funcionalidades também” -
              2022
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="comment text-center flex-center flex align-center flex-column"
          >
            <h4 class="font-lg font-bold underline comment-title">
              Fernando Brandão
            </h4>
            <div class="comment-body font-xsm">
              “O conteudo do site está completo e as funcionalidades também” -
              2022
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="comment comment-main flex-center flex-column flex">
            <h4 class="title-1 font-bold underline comment-title main">
              Guilherme Delfino
            </h4>
            <div class="comment-body main font-md">
              “Eu adorei o site! Nele eu posso saber dos conteudo do personagem
              e ainda entendo um pouco mais do autor!” - 2022
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="comment text-center flex-center flex align-center flex-column"
          >
            <h4 class="font-lg font-bold underline comment-title">Dan</h4>
            <div class="comment-body font-xsm">
              “O site tem as funcionalidades e os quesitos de socioemocional” -
              2022
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="comment text-center flex-center flex align-center flex-column"
